  Ti7 Kiam5-pou-a2 u7 chit8 e5 chi2-moe7, tui3 33 ni5 cheng5 kau3 hian7-chai7, siu7 chhoa7 kui2-na7 pai2 khi3 khoaN3 thian-tong5 te7-gek8 e5 su7, po3 hou7 tai7-ke chai. Chit e5 chi2-moe7 20 hoe3 cho3 chhin ti7 chhau2-te7, tui3 an2-ni loe2-chi3 leng2-sim, ti3-kau3 u7 phang7 thang hou7 Mou5-kui2 chhim-jip8. Sat-tan3 na7 lai5 ka7 i chhoa7--khi3, i chiu7 hun7--khi3, in pe7-bo2 na7 pek-chhiat ki5-to2, i chiu7 koh ho2--khi2-lai5. 
  U7 chit8 jit8, chit8 e5 lau7-lang5 lai5 ka7 i chhoa7 khi3 peh chit8 e5 un2-ku kio5, khi2-thau5 teh peh chin ho2-se3, kau3 au7-lai5 teh peh khok8-khok8 hian2, kau3 beh poah8--loh8-khi3; i chin kiaN, m7-kaN2 peh. Lau7-lang5 chiu7 ka7 i kong2, ¡§Goa2 khan3 li2, m7-bian2 kiaN,¡¨ i chiu7 koh ka7 i kong2, ¡§Li2 khi2-thau5 teh peh chin ho2-se3; che chiu7-si7 lang5 na7 jiat8-sim teh peh long2 chin chai7, na7 leng2-sim e5 si5 teh peh chiu7 e7 hian2, beh poah8--loh8-khi3.¡¨ In peh koe3 hit e5 kio5 chiu7 tit8-tit8 kiaN5. Koh kau3 chit8 e5 kio5 chin tng5, koe3-khi3 hit peng5 u7 chit8 chiah sai pak8 ti7 hia, peh khi2-lai5 kiaN5-lai5 kiaN5-khi3. I chin kiaN, m7-kaN2 koe3, hit lang5 chiu7 koh ka7 i aN5 hit chiah sai, i chiu7 siam2 koe3-khi3. Koh tit8-tioh8 kiaN5 kau3 chit8 khu koe2-chi2 hng5, u7 thiaN-kiN3 chin ho2 thiaN e5 siaN-im, koh khoaN3-kiN3 chin che7 seng3-tou5 ti7 hia teh ban2 koe2-chi2 lai5 chiah8. I khoaN3 liau2 chin hoaN2-hi2, ia7 ai3 ka7 i bong khoaN3--leh, chong2-si7 bong long2 bo5. 
  Au7-lai5 in chiu7 koh kiaN5 kau3 seng3-siaN5 mng5-khau2, hut-jian5 Chu2 Ia5-sou kap thiN-sai3 chhoa7 chit8 e5 sin3-tou5 beh jip8-khi3 seng3-siaN5, in chiu7 siam2 ti7 siaN5-mng5 piN hou7 in koe3-khi3. Hit e5 lang5 si7 tu2-a2 tui3 se3-kan siu7 chhoa7--lai5 e5, sou2 chheng7 e5 saN bai2-bai2, koh bin7 ia7 si7 bo5 sui2, san2-san2. Ti7 hia u7 chit8 khut po2-choaN5 chui2, i chiu7 loh8-khi3 se2 seng-khu, hit si5 tui3 seng3-siaN5 e5 lai7-bin7 u7 chit8 e5 lang5 theh8 chit8 su peh8-saN te2 ti7 chit8 e5 kim poaN5-a2, phang5 chhut-lai5 ka7 i chheng7. Hit si5 hit e5 lang5 hut-jian5 kap i2-cheng5 long2 bo5 sio-siang5, pian3 chit8 e5 chin eng5-kng koh chin sui2 e5 lang5. Ti7 siaN5-lai7 u7 chit8 tin7 chin kou2-chui e5 gin2-a2 chhut-lai5 ngia5-chih i jip8-khi3; in si7 tui3 tang-mng5 jip8-khi3. Au7-lai5 goan2 chiu7 tui3 lam5-mng5 jip8-khi3, kau3 mng5-khau2, mng5 phah khui u7 eng5-kng chio3--chhut-lai5. Goa2 hou7 hit e5 kng chio3--tioh8, goa2 chiu7 to3-the3 chin kiaN, m7-kaN2 jip8-khi3, hit lang5 ka7 goa2 kong2, Li2 u7 toa3 choe7 lai5, chiah e7 kiaN. Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni, saN-pai2 hou7 kng chio3, goa2 long2 to3-the3, m7-kaN2 jip8-khi3; au7-lai5 i chiah khan goa2 e5 chhiu2 jip8--khi3. 
  Seng3-siaN5 e5 lai7-bin7 ke-lou7 long2 phou kim, chhu3 si7 kng-liang7 e5 po2-chioh8 lai5 khi2 e5, tak8 keng pang5-keng long2 chin sui2. Goan2 jip8-khi3 e5 si5, tak8 e5 lang5 long2 teh chiah8 mih8, tak8 e5 long2 teh khoaN3 goa2, siuN7-tioh8 ka-ki7 e5 seng-khu kap lang5 bo5 sio-siang5, chin kian3-siau3, m7-kaN2 kiah8 thau5 khi2-lai5 khoaN3 lang5. Goa2 chiu7 thau5-khak chhih-chhih tit8-tit8 koe3--khi3. 
  Kau3 goa2 e5 pang5-keng, i ka7 goa2 kong2, Chit keng si7 li2 e5, goa2 chiu7 chin hoaN-hi2 beh tiam3 ti7 hia; bin5-chhng5 si7 po2-chioh8 lai5 cho3 e5, piah-nih u7 tiau3 chit8 su eng5-kng chhan3-lan7 sui2 e5 peh8-saN, chhiu2 chhun khi3 beh ka7 i bong, bong bo5, beh che7 bin5-chhng5 ia7 che7 bo5, in-ui7 si5 iau2-be7 kau3. Hit lang5 chiu7 tit8-tit8 ka7 goa2 koaN2, kio3 goa2 tioh8 koh toe3 i khi3. Goa2 in3 i kong2, M7 ah, beh tiam3 chia chiu7 ho2, bo5 ai3 koh khi3 pat8 ui7. I kong2, be7 sai2-tit, tioh8 kin2-kin2 chhut-lai5 khi3, in-ui7 li2 e5 si5 iau2-be7 kau3, koaN2-kin2 chhut-lai5 khi3, na7 bo5 siaN5-mng5, teh-beh koaiN lah. Au7-lai5 goa2 hou7 i kiong5-pek, chiu7 koh kap i khi3. 
  Goan2 nng7 e5 kiaN2 kau3 chit8 e5 chhim-ian e5 sou2-chai7, i chiu7 chhun chhiu2 khan goa2 poe koe3--khi3, hit lai7-bin7 u7 thi5-khau3 ai-chham2 e5 siaN, koh u7 khoaN3-kiN3 ou-ian tui3 lai7-te2 tit8-tit8 chheng3--chhut-lai5, goa2 chiu7 mng7 khoaN3 he siaN2-hoe3? I in3 goa2 kong2, Che si7 cha2-cheng5 e5 phaiN2 sin5 tiam3 ti7 hia teh heng5-hoat8 e5 sou2-chai7. Koh kau3 chit8 e5 sou2-chai7 chhin-chhiuN7 bong7 chin toa7-e5, ia7 chin che7. Goa2 chiu7 koh mng7, he siaN2-hoe3? I kong2, hit lai7-bin7 ia7 si7 teh heng5-hoat8 lang5. Koh kau3 chit8 sou2-chai7 khoaN3-kiN3 chheng-chheng ban7-ban7 chho2-chho2 e5 lang5 be7 sng3-tit; u7-e5 chheng7 chin sui2, u7-e5 chheng7 chin bai2, u7-e5 thau5-mng5 kim-kim, u7-e5 thau5-mng5 sam3-sam3, ti7 chit8 e5 toa7 e5 chhau2-pou e5 sou2-chai7. Goa2 khoaN3 liau2 chin siong-sim, in-ui7 in long2 bo5 chhu3 thang khia7, goa2 mng7 he si7 an2-choaN2-iuN7? Thai3 tiam3 ti7 hia? I in3 kong2, hiah e5 lang5 teh theng3-hau7 sim2-phoaN3. 
  Goan2 koh kiaN5, khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 e5 soaN u7 hoe2 teh toh8, ia7 u7 chit8-tin7 chit8-tin7 e5 lang5 ti7 hia teh theng3-hau7 beh loh8-khi3 hoe2-nih sio, in-ui7 hoe2-lai7 e5 lang5 na7 sio liau2 khi2-lai5, chiu7 koh oaN7 pat8 tin7 e5 lang5 loh8-khi3 sio, an2-ni sio the3 teh heng5-hoat8. Goa2 khoaN3 ti7 hoe2-lai7 e5 lang5 sio kau3 ge5-a2 giang3-giang3, goa2 chin kiaN, chiu7 ka7 i kong2, goa2 m7-kaN2 khoaN3, chin kiaN, i chiu7 ka7 goa2 kong2, li2 na7 kiaN, khan goa2 e5 saN-a2-ku khi3 am li2 e5 bak8-chiu. Goa2 chiu7 koaN2-kin2 khiu2 i e5 saN lai5 am, liam5-piN kau3 goa2 e5 chhu3 cheng-sin5 khi2--lai5. Chong2-si7 bak8-chiu long2 bu7-bu7 khoaN3 be7 beng5, ke-lai7 e5 lang5 kap chhu3-piN, chhin-lang5 long2 chau2 lai5 khoaN3, sio-cheN mng7, li2 tng2-lai5 lah, li2 u7 khoaN3-tioh8 goa2 bou2-lang5 a2-bo5? Goa2 tu2-a2 hun7-khi3 3 jit8 nng7 mi5. Hit si5 lang5 na7 mng7 goa2 khoaN3 goan2 bou2-lang5 u7 tit-kiu3 a2-bo5? Chiu7 thau5-khak teng2 u7 kng-kng e5 sou2-chai7, koh u7 chit8 lang5 khia7 ti7 hia teh in3, ka7 i kong2 u7 ouh! u7 tit-kiu3 ti7 chia, an2-ni kau3 am3, chiu7 bo5 koh khoaN3-kiN3, bak8-chiu chiu7 e7 thi2 kim. 
  Hit si5 ke-lai7 e5 lang5 kong2 beh chu2 moe5 hou7 goa2 chiah8, goan2 lau7-pe7 kong2, m7-thang, hiah ku2 bo5 chiah8 kiaN-liau2 e7 gui5-hiam2, chiah8 am2 khah ho2. Goa2 chiu7 kap goan2 hiaN-so2 teh kong2, chit si5 na7 lai5 si2 iau2 e7 tit-kiu3, na7 au7-jit8 lai5 si2 m7-chai e7 a2-be7? iau2 m7-chai. Tu2 teh kong2 e5 si5, hut-jian5 khoaN3-kiN3 thiN-sai3 kap Chu2 Ia5-sou lai5 beh chhoa7 goa2 khi3, chhiu2-nih u7 phang5 chit8 e5 kim-poe, kio3 i chhun chhiu2 khi3 chih. Goa2 toa7 siaN kong2, Chu2 lai5 lah, kio3 goa2 chhun chhiu2 khi3 chih poe. Goan2 lau7-pe7 thiaN-tioh8, kin2-kin2 chau2 lai5 tui3 Chu2 kiu5 kong2, Chu2 ah, m7-thang chit si5 chhoa7 i to3-khi3, kiaN-liau2 si2 e5 mia5 e7 tu2-tioh8 ki-chhi3, hou7 lang5 hui2-pong3, an2-ni pek-chhiat tui3 Chu2 tit8-tit8 kiu5. Au7-lai5 Chu2 kap thiN-sai3 bin7 oat8 koe3-khi3, chiu7 tit8-tit8 kiaN5-khi3. Goa2 ka7 goan2 pa5 kong2, Chu2 to3-khi3 lah. Tui3 hit si5 goa2 chiu7 ho2--khi2-lai5. 
  Ti7 15, 6 ni5 cheng5 ai3 chhut ti7 Kau3-hoe7-po3, hou7 tai7-ke cho3 chham-kho2, tu2-tioh8 Tai7-tang-a chian3-cheng, Peh8-oe7-ji7 (Kong-po3-sia7) soa3 theng5-pan2, tui3 an2-ni bo5 thang in3, ian5-chhian5 kau3 kin-a2-jit8. Au7-jit8 u7 ki-hoe7 beh koh sia2, in-ui7 ti7 chit chap8-goa7 ni5 ku2 koh siu7 chhoa7 khi3 khoaN3 chin che7 pai2. 
  1953 ni5 4 goeh8 23 jit8, Chu2 e5 su3-chia2 koh lai5 tui3 chit e5 chi2-moe7 kong2, ¡§Khi2-lai5, m7-thang khun3, goa2 chhoa7 li2 chhut-lai5 khi3 khoaN3-khoaN3 le3,¡¨ nng7 lang5 chiu7 khi3 kau3 chit8 e5 sou2-chai7, chiu7 pang3 i ka-ki7 chit8-lang5 kau3 nng7-choa7 chhin-chhiuN7 chioh8-thau5 sou2 thiap8, ou-ou bai2-bai2 beh-to2 beh-to2 e5 chhu3. I chiu7 tui3 tiong-ng tit8-tit8 ka7 i kiaN5 jip8-khi3, hit lai7-bin7 ou-am3, koh chhin-chhiuN7 ta3-bong5 bu7-bu7 bo5 khoaN3-tioh8 thau5-cheng5, ti7 liong2-peng5 e5 pang5-keng long2 u7 siaN teh hoah kong2, ¡§Khiu2-le3, liah8-le3 m7-thang hou7 i chau2-khi3, khah-kin2 khah-kin2 ka7 i liah8-le3, m7-thang hou7 chau2-khi3, toh-a2 kha chhoe7 khoaN3 mai7 le3, bin5-chhng5 kha chhoe7 khoaN3-le3. ¡¨ 
  Liah8--le3 liah8--le3, i thiaN tioh8 chit e5 siaN kiaN kau3 chau2 bo5 lou7, tit8-tit8 ai3 chau2 chhut-khi3, chong2-si7 lai7-bin7 long2 ou-thiN te7-am3, na7 kau3 hou7-teng7 chiu7 tui3 teng2-bin7 u7 tam7-poh8 kng pang3 loh8-lai5 hou7 i khoaN3, i chiu7 koe3 hou7-teng7 koh tit8-tit8 chau2, beh chau2 chhut-khi3, lai7-bin7 e5 siaN koh tit8-tit8 beh jiong2 i, chiu7 koh tit8-tit8 beh chau2 chhut-khi3, na7 koh kau3 hou7-teng7 e5 sou2-chai7, chiu7 koh u7 kng lai5 ka7 i chio3. An2-ni kui2-na7 pai2, au7-lai5 chiu7 chau2 chhut goa7-bin7, i koh beh chau2 e5 si5, hut-jian5 ti7 au7-bin7 u7 siaN teh ka7 i kong2, m7-thang chau2, i chiu7 oat8 koe3-lai5, khoaN3-tioh8 Chu2 e5 su3-chia2, i chiu7 tui3 i kong2, ¡§Li2 ia7 thang pang3 goa2 chit8-lang5 hiam2-hiam2 hou7 i liah8-khi3,¡¨ i in3 kong2, m7-si7 beh liah8 li2, i chiu7 koh mng7 kong2, bo5, si7 beh liah8 sim2-mih8 lang5? tit8-tit8 hoah ui5 hoah liah8, goa2 kiaN kau3 chau2 bo5 lou7, i in3 kong2, he si7 khah cha2 khun2-tiok8 Ki-tok-tou5 hiah e5 phaiN2-lang5 koaiN ti7 hia teh ka7 i heng5-hoat8, na7 teh heng5-hoat8, in chiu7 phun2-phun2 hoat-chhut cha2 teh liah8 lang5 e5 siaN-im chhut-lai5, m7-si7 beh liah8 li2, goa2 iu5-goan5 u7 kap li2 ti7-teh, li2 na7 beh koe3 hou7-teng7 goa2 chiu7 pang3 chit8-sut-a2 kng ka7 li2 chio3. 
  TaN lan2 koh chin3-cheng5 lai5-khi3, kau3 chit8 e5 oat-kak, u7 khoaN3 chit8 e5 cha-bou2 lang5, tham3 chit8-e7, kiu jip8-khi3, i chiu7 mng7 kong2, he siaN2-he3? I in3 kong2, hit e5 lang5 teh khoaN3 lang5 e5 sim-lai7, na7 bo5 Chu2 e5 Sin5, i chiu7 beh jip8 khi3. Au7-lai5 koh kiaN5 kau3 chit8 sou2-chai7, khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 lang5 chhiu2 theh8 Seng3-keng kap Si beh khi3 le2-pai3, koh khoaN3 chit8 e5 kui2 lai5 teh ka7 i khiu2, i chiu7 kap i phah, khah theng5 koh chit8 e5 kui2 lai5, koh kap i teh phah, au7-lai5 chiu7 hou7 in tiong-kan chit8 e5 khiu2-khi3, koh chin3-cheng5 teh kiaN5, koh khoaN3-kiN3 chit8-lang5 chhiu2 theh8 Seng3-keng kap Si, koh khoaN3-kiN3 nng7 e5 kui2 oa2-lai5 teh ka7 i khiu2, hit lang5 khoaN3 phah be7 iaN5 i, chiu7 ki5-to2, ¡§Chu2 ah, kiu3 goa2,¡¨ Chu2 oa2 lai5, hit nng7 e5 kui2 chiu7 chau2, chin3-cheng5 koh kiaN5, khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 e5 lang5 sin-piN u7 chit8 e5 lang5 giah8 chit8-ki koaiN2-a2 khia7 teh, koh khah theng5 nng7-e5 kui2 lai5 teh kap i sio-phah, chit e5 chi2-moe7 chiu7 tui3 Chu2 e5 su3-chia2 kong2, piN-a2 hit e5 lang5 thai2 m7 kin2-kin2 ka7 i ui7, thai2 beh pang3 hou7 hit nng7 e5 kui2 ka7 i phah kau3 an2-ni; i in3 kong2, li2 tiam7-tiam7, koh khoaN3, kau3 au7-lai5 hit e5 lang5 chai i phah su i, chiu7 toa7-siaN kiu5 kong2, ¡§Chu2 ah! Kiu3 goa2,¡¨ piN-a2 e5 lang5 chiah giah8 i e5 koaiN2-a2 khi2-lai5, hit nng7 e5 kui2 chiu7 chau2 khi3. I khoaN3 kau3 chia chiu7 tit8-tit8 chin3-cheng5 teh khi3, hut-jian5 tu2-tioh8 chit8-lang5 aN3-loh8 khi3 khoaN3 i e5 bin7 kong2, li2 toaN-sin chhut-goa7 mah? I long2 bo5 liah8 cho3 sim2-mih8 i3-su3, koh theng5 tiap-a2-ku2, tui3 au7-bin7 u7 lang5 lai5 teh ka7 i khiu2-saN, i oat8 koe3-khi3, khoaN3-tioh8 nng7 e5 kui2, i chiu7 tit8-tit8 kap i sio-phah, koh khiu2 kui2 e5 chhiu2 lai5 ka7 i ka7 kui2 e5 bah pho3-pho3, ka7-tioh8 koh bo5 lau5 hoeh, i chiu7 phui3 hiat-kak8, chhau3-chhiN chhau3-chhiN, koh ka7 i ka7, koh phui3 hiat-kak8. 
  An2-ni kap in phah liau2 khoaN3 be7 iaN5--in, chiu7 ki5-to2 kong2: ¡§Chu2--ah! Kiu3--goa2.¡¨ Chu2 e5 su3-chia2 chiu7 lai5, i chiu7 ka7 i kong2, li2 ia7 thang an2-ni pang3 goa2 chit8 e5 hiam2-hiam2 hou7 in thoa--khi3, i chiu7 mng7 i kong2: ¡§Ti7 lou7 tiong li2 u7 tu2 tioh8 chit8 e5 lang5 iah bo5?¡¨ In3 kong2: ¡§U7, hit lang5 tui3 li2 kong2 sim2-mih?¡¨ I kong2: ¡§Li2 tan-sin chhut-goa7 mah? An2-ni li2 phah m7 kiN3 Chu2, li2 iau2-ku2 m7 chai-iaN2 thang chhoe7. TaN li2 tioh8 to2--khi3, si5-si5 khek-khek khiN5 tiau5 ti7 Chu2, tioh8 si5-si5 thak8 Seng3-keng ki5-to2 kiat-lian5 ti7 Chu2, m7-thang phah m7-kiN3 Chu2, lang5 na7 tan-sin chhut-goa7 chin gui5-hiam2.¡¨ TaN chit e5 chi2-moe7 ka7 goa2 kong2, i na7 teh leng2-sim sit-chi3 e5 si5, Chu2 e5 su3-chia2 chiu7 e7 chhoa7 i khi3 khoaN3-khoaN3--le3, thang ka3-si7 i, che ia7-si7 chin thang cho3 lan2 e5 chham-kho2. 
